snippet.textDisplay: Not an easy task to pull off an arrangement like this, but the studio band has done it with immense ease and utter perfection. Such a beautiful and soothing composition amazingly executed by both Mai Dhai and Atif Aslam. I feel that Mai Dhai is our asset and should be promoted more on international stage. Atif Aslam is a rare born talent and he proves it yet again with this track! Majestic! Kudos, team.
